                        <p>Reach thousands of Indian community members who actively seek Indian products and services</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <h4>üì¢ Deal Promotions</h4>
                        <p>Create and post exclusive deals to attract more customers and increase sales</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <h4>üì± Digital Presence</h4>
                        <p>Professional business listing with contact details, location, and service descriptions</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <h4>üí¨ Customer Engagement</h4>
                        <p>Direct communication with customers through our integrated messaging system</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <h4>üìä Business Analytics</h4>
                        <p>Track deal performance, customer engagement, and business growth metrics</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-card">
                        <h4>ü§ù Community Support</h4>
                        <p>Be part of a supportive business network that promotes Indian entrepreneurship</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="quick-start">
                <h3>Quick Start Guide</h3>
                <ol class="steps-list">
                    <li><strong>Complete Your Profile:</strong> Add business description, contact details, and high-quality photos</li>
                    <li><strong>Create Your First Deal:</strong> Post an attractive offer to draw in customers</li>
                    <li><strong>Set Business Hours:</strong> Let customers know when you're open</li>
                    <li><strong>Add Location Details:</strong> Make it easy for customers to find you</li>
                    <li><strong>Engage with Community:</strong> Respond to customer inquiries promptly</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        
            
            <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0; border-left: 4px solid #FF9933;">
                <h4 style="color: #FF9933; margin-bottom: 15px;">üí° Pro Tips for Success:</h4>
                <ul style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Post deals regularly to keep customers engaged</li>
                    <li>Use high-quality images for your business and deals</li>
                    <li>Respond quickly to customer redemption requests</li>
                    <li>Keep your business information updated</li>
                    <li>Participate in community events and festivals</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Welcome to the Indians in Ghana Business Community!</strong></p>
            <p>We're here to help your business thrive. Contact us anytime for support.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Indians in Ghana Business Directory</p>
                <p>Email: support@indiansinghana.com</p>
                <p>Business Support: business@indiansinghana.com</p>
                <p>This email was sent to {{email}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
